1. *Pitaš* li se da li ćeš uspeti? (Are you asking yourself if you will succeed?)
2. On *pitaju* ga da li je spreman da se pridruži. (They are asking him if he is ready to join.)
3. *Pita* li ga tata zašto je tako čudno ponašanje? (Is his dad asking him why the behaviour is so strange?)
4. Ona *pitaše* ga da li želi da ide. (She asked him if he wanted to go.)
5. *Pitaju* li ga očevi o njegovim planovima za budućnost? (Are his parents asking him about his plans for the future?)